data.description: Sitting on a .62 acre lot in between Stillman Valley and Byron this property is in an excellent subdivision. Entering in the home you have a large family room with picture window. Off the family room you have an eat-in kitchen with sliding door access to the oversized deck. Down the hall you have a full bathroom with jacuzzi tub. 3 large bedrooms that are all good sizes. Master bedroom has a half bathroom. Downstairs you have tons of potential for a rec room/bar area with lots of unfinished storage space. Deep garage with room for storage and work bench. Popular Meridian 223 school district. Quick access to US-20 and I-39.  Seller is offering 5k in closing costs to buyer at closing.
